# PartyKit local dev secrets — copy to .dev.vars and fill in values.
# .dev.vars is gitignored; never commit real keys.
#
# Get your fal.ai key at https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
# Without this key, the room server uses MockMusicGenerator (returns a mock URL
# immediately; the browser won't play audio but the full message flow is exercised).
FAL_KEY=
